data.description: What a gem with county taxes only! This 4-BD/2 BATH brick home won’t last long! This home is located in a gated community, and offers hardwood flooring, great natural light, and a beautiful kitchen w/granite countertops, breakfast bar, ss appliances, and an eat-in dining space. Spacious primary bedroom w/bathroom ensuite w/granite double vanity, spacious shower, and garden bathtub. Laundry room, low-maintenance yard, and a neutral color palette throughout the home. Book your tour today!
